GraphData.Name: Calibration Focus
GraphData.Kommentar: The graph generates a segment to weld according to the current seam number. The parameters must be provided to the ScanmasterFocusPoint filter, and just copied to all the seams in a product (no need to define the scanner position or remove the seams at the end of the product)
